// FILE     : ProcessFinishedMessage.java
// PURPOSE  : What to do when the process finishes.
// AUTHOR   : David Jones
// MODIFIED : Andrew Newman
// HISTORY  : 24/03/96   Created
//          : 01/07/96   Uses Memory
//          : 03/08/97   Moved to message system
